<!-- Button trigger modal -->
<button type="button" class="btn mr-1 px-2 py-1" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#fastElevatorsModal">
<i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
</button>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal" id="fastElevatorsModal" tabindex="-1">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5">Fast elevators</h1>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>If enabled, Samus moves up and down elevators at a faster speed.</p>

        <p>This also has an effect of reducing the total heat damage taken while on elevators. For example, it makes it more likely
        to be able to survive an unexpected trip down the Lower Norfair Main Hall elevator, which takes 47 energy in each direction 
        with this option enabled, compared to 109 energy with it disabled.</p>

        <p><i>Patch by Lioran.</i></p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
